name: Fake Coin Cave
description:
Made for Brackeys's Game Jam February 2022; Theme: It is not real

The coins that spin to the right are real coins: take them; but avoid the coins that spin to the left for they are fake.

Control: Arrow Keys

Been a while since I last made a game I had to relearn a lot of things so the game ended up having less than I planned.

In any case, have fun! :3
